  "comment": "Xpression 2000S is a bright, medium-sized LED moving head with a beam angle of 17deg and an output of 4488 lumens, suitable for indoor venues. It features a dichroic color wheel with 7 colors + open, an indexed, bi-rotational metal gobo wheel with 6 gobos + open, and dual prisms - a 12-facet circular prism and a 10-facet linear prism, that can be overlaid and rotated for dynamic effects. Other features include a frost effect, motorized focus, precise 16-bit pan and tilt and adjustable PWM (1,200 - 15,000 Hz). All colour and gobo effects are perfectly matched across the Xpression series, ensuring seamless integration with other fixtures in the range.\n\nControl modes include DMX/RDM, master/slave, manual, auto, built-in program, and stand alone. Custom programming allows you to create and save your own presets, eliminating the need for an external controller for small events. The included quick lock can be adjusted to multiple positions for flexible mounting. The base features an ergonomic handle, enhancing both functionality and the overall stylish design.",
